    - **Consider**: BMO Balanced ETF (ZBAL.TO, MER = 0.20%), iShares Core Balanced ETF Portfolio (XBAL.TO, MER = 0.20%), and Vanguard Balanced ETF Portfolio (VBAL.TO, MER = 0.24%).
